  &lt;p id="FX7vct"&gt;Former President Donald Trump &lt;a href="https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/posts/112941157610530127"&gt;confirmed his campaign&lt;/a&gt; was hacked just hours after &lt;a href="https://www.politico.com/news/2024/08/10/trump-campaign-hack-00173503"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Politico &lt;/em&gt;revealed it had been sent&lt;/a&gt; internal documents from the campaign. In &lt;a href="https://www.cnn.com/2024/08/10/politics/trump-campaign-blames-iran-for-hack/index.html"&gt;a statement to CNN&lt;/a&gt;, Trump campaign spokesperson Steven Cheung said, “These documents were obtained illegally from foreign sources hostile to the United States, intended to interfere with the 2024 election.”&lt;/p&gt;
