    <title>The next iPhone SE could have Apple Intelligence, which says a lot</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="A picture of the iPhone 14 laying on a glass surface." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0G45h2E_R8D_T00sOVUskhMnf0Y=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73514957/226270_IPHONE_14_REGULAR_PHO_akrales_0736.0.jpg" /&gt;
